An entire generation of children was born without thumbs,

107
00:04:31,737 --> 00:04:33,539
a phenomenon known to locals as...

108
00:04:33,872 --> 00:04:36,474
-"The Situation." -(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

109
00:04:36,574 --> 00:04:38,043
And, incidentally,

110
