as one local new-station reported,

226
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:15,053
with an almost prideful tone.

227
00:09:15,788 --> 00:09:18,423
ANCHOR:<i> The most contaminated  place in the entire</i>

228
00:09:18,523 --> 00:09:21,226
<i> Western Hemisphere isn't  at a polluting factory</i>

229
00:09:21,326 --> 00:09:22,961
<i> or an old chemical plant.</i>

230
00:09:23,229 --> 00:09:25,264
<i> It's right here  in Washington State.</i>

231
00:09:25,364 --> 00:09:26,598
(AUDIENCE LAUGHS) Oh!

232
00:09:26,697 --> 00:09:28,600
"It's right here! We did it guys!

