00:09:28,966 --> 00:09:32,037
Washington State, home to the most contaminated place

234
00:09:32,136 --> 00:09:33,571
in the Western Hemisphere,

235
00:09:34,004 --> 00:09:35,807
thousands of acres of apple orchards,

236
00:09:36,008 --> 00:09:39,845
and several of Ted Bundy's grizzliest murders. We did it!

237
00:09:40,177 --> 00:09:41,179
Right here!"

238
